display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex> but not a submodule of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li>
<fr:li>If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathop {\textrm {Ann}}\nolimits _{R}(M)]]></fr:tex> is a two-sided ideal of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex>, then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M[\mathop {\textrm {Ann}}\nolimits _{R}(M)]]]></fr:tex> is a submodule of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex>.</fr:li></fr:ol>
 
   
